WEBVTT

00:02:29.231 --> 00:02:31.832
which must seem like some sort of newfangled thing

00:02:31.832 --> 00:02:35.360
that "back in my day," they never had.

00:02:35.360 --> 00:02:37.210
So when Granny pulls out her smart phone

00:02:37.210 --> 00:02:39.148
to post pictures of her dentures

00:02:39.148 --> 00:02:40.530
or her grandkids,

00:02:40.530 --> 00:02:42.759
irony ensues.

00:02:42.759 --> 00:02:46.473
Reasonable expectations of the situation are not met.

00:02:46.473 --> 00:02:48.354
That is irony.

00:02:48.354 --> 00:02:51.316
So while the cake dropper might not be ironic,

00:02:51.316 --> 00:02:55.297
there are all kinds of situations in life that are.

00:02:55.297 --> 00:02:59.126
Go out, and find those true examples of irony.